---
import DownloadButton from "./DownloadButton.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 items-start">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium tracking-widest uppercase text-white">
      About
    </h2>

    <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#8c8c8c] leading-relaxed">
      I build websites and web applications using
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> React</span> and
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> Astro</span>, alongside legacy projects in
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> WordPress</span> and PHP.
    </p>

    <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#8c8c8c] leading-relaxed">
      Currently, I am actively expanding my skills into backend development, focusing on
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> C# .NET</span>, SQL databases, and containerization with
      <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]"> Docker</span>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-xl font-light text-[#8c8c8c] leading-relaxed">
      My experience as a <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]">QA Tester</span> and <span class="text-[#F8F8F8]">Team Test Lead</span> teaches me to approach development with code quality and reliability in mind, ensuring applications hold up under real-world usage.
    </p>

    <DownloadButton
      href="./curriculum_vitae_alessio_pinto.pdf"
      label="Download resume"
    />
  </div>
</section>
